    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_5132261510040123190.png",
                "id": "talent91097",
                "key": "重鉗碎擊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "重鉗碎擊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>；如果本角色附屬有至少7層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span>，則此傷害+1。<br>然後，本角色附屬2層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">護盾</span><br>每層提供1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>，保護所附屬角色。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/0ae22e52af3cd0693c58a452cef1d284_3644023741379526663.png",
                "id": "talent31802",
                "key": "烈焰燃綻",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "烈焰燃綻"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>本角色準備技能：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">熾烈轟破</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">熾烈轟破</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span><br>（需準備1個行動輪）<br>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，對敵方所有後臺角色造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span>。本角色每附屬有2層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span>，就使此技能造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>+1。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">護盾</span><br>每層提供1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>，保護所附屬角色。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/a9c20ff9f809e176b5b49857c4ad1153_6126854181707412636.png",
                "id": "talent40495",
                "key": "戰陣爆轟",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "戰陣爆轟"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>【被動】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">戰鬥開始時：</span>初始附屬5層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方執行任意行動後：</span>如果我方場上存在重甲蟹殼以外的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>狀態或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>出戰狀態，則將其全部移除；每移除1個，就使角色附屬2層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹殼</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">護盾</span><br>每層提供1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>，保護所附屬角色。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/926ad2c8e8892093800da58cea01f2ad_4884538393764846335.png",
                "id": "talent60223",
                "key": "帝王甲冑",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "帝王甲冑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_8798649460765508169.png",
                "id": "talent53728",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4080898523686242701.png",
                "id": "talent74105",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_3096117584019351748.png",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span></strong></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p><p>規則解釋加上</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備技能</span></strong></p><p>有些技能無法直接使用，而是需要一定次數的行動輪來進行<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>。</p><p>輪到一位牌手行動時，如果該牌手的「出戰角色」正在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>技能，則跳過該牌手的行動；如果技能已經完成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>，角色將會在此時直接使用此技能。（此類需要<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>的技能，無法觸發「使用技能後」「角色引發元素反應後」等效果。）</p><p>只有「出戰角色」才能<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>技能的「出戰角色」被切換到後臺，技能的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備</span>就會被打斷。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></strong></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/13/142229365/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8075617730286378704.png",
                "id": "talent41606",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
